Environment: Next.js 15 App Router app at tasks.meavo.app ‚Äî Meavo team task management (inbox + kanban boards). Satellite of the meavo-gateway ecosystem on a shared Neon Postgres.

## Stack

- Next.js 15 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 3
- Prisma 6 via `@meavo/db` (shared Neon Postgres, schema owned by the meavo-db repo)
- NextAuth v5 JWT ‚Äî Credentials + invite-only Google, gated on the Tasks tool card
- `@meavo/navigation` shared top nav; hosted on Vercel

## Do NOT

- Edit the Prisma schema here ‚Äî it lives in **meavo-db**; bump the `@meavo/db` git ref in `package.json`
- Run `prisma db push` (intentionally disabled ‚Äî shared DB)
- Write to other apps' tables (`Deal`, `FactoryProductionBatch`, `RpRequest`, `Assembly`) ‚Äî read-only for link resolution
- Look up the tool card by `linkedAppKey` ‚Äî use `TASKS_CARD_ID` from `src/lib/tasks-config.ts`
- Import `src/lib/auth.ts` in `middleware.ts` (edge) ‚Äî use `src/lib/auth.config.ts`
- Add external component libraries (shadcn/Radix/MUI) ‚Äî use `src/components/ui.tsx`
- Build a custom top nav ‚Äî shell comes from `@meavo/navigation`
- Skip `CRON_SECRET` auth on `/api/cron/*`
- Commit secrets or `.env.local`

## Code layout

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Authenticated pages | `src/app/(app)/` ‚Äî inbox `page.tsx`, `boards/`, `settings/` |
| Public login | `src/app/login/` |
| Server Actions (mutations) | `src/app/actions/` |
| API routes (auth, cron, health only) | `src/app/api/` |
| Domain logic (authz, queries, bootstrap) | `src/lib/domain/` |
| Integrations (Slack, Todoist, cross-app links) | `src/lib/integrations/` |
| Per-user settings & digests | `src/lib/settings/` |
| Auth & tool-card gate | `src/lib/auth.ts`, `src/lib/access.ts`, `src/middleware.ts` |
| UI kit + feature components | `src/components/` (`ui.tsx`, `modal.tsx`) |
| Tests | N/A ‚Äî no test suite |

## Data flow

```
Browser ‚Üí Server Action (src/app/actions/*)
        ‚Üí getTasksUser() gate ‚Üí task-authz check ‚Üí Prisma (@meavo/db ‚Üí shared Neon)
        ‚Üí revalidatePath()
Vercel cron (weekdays 07:00) ‚Üí /api/cron/* ‚Üí Prisma ‚Üí Slack webhook
```

Slack side effects are fire-and-forget (`.catch(console.error)`). Email must be enqueued to `NotificationOutbox` (`src/lib/notifications/enqueue.ts`) ‚Äî only gateway sends.

